Day 43: Docker Ports Mapping

Date: October 8, 2025
Overview
Mastered port mapping for container accessibility.
Key Concepts Learned

Port publishing
Host port vs container port
Port binding to specific interfaces
Dynamic port assignment

Commands Used
bashdocker run -p 8080:80 nginx
docker run -p 127.0.0.1:8080:80 nginx
docker port container_name

Challenges Faced
Port conflicts when multiple containers tried to use the same host port. Had to plan port allocation carefully.
